Edgars will be offering great deals on Samsung A-series smartphones this Black Friday. These smartphones are known for offering tremendous value for their price – meaning these Black Friday deals are an absolute bargain. “We are committed to bridging the gap between flagship features and affordability. I believe the Galaxy A Series offers the best value in its segment,” said Samsung South Africa Director of Integrated Mobility Justin Hume. Click here to buy a Samsung Galaxy A-series smartphone from Edgars. Edgars is offering three great deals on Samsung Galaxy A-series smartphones – the A11, A21s, and A30s. The Samsung Galaxy A11 offers impressive features at an affordable price. These features include a 6.4-inch display, a triple-lens camera array, 15W fast charging, a 4,000mAh battery, and an octa-core processor. The Samsung Galaxy A21s sports a quad-lens camera system with a 48MP primary lens – the sort of specifications that are usually reserved for flagship smartphones which cost in excess of R10,000. Other key features include a 5,000mAh battery and a 13MP front camera that is housed within a punch hole display. The Samsung Galaxy A30s is the most powerful of these smartphones and has an impressive triple-lens camera system. It also features a 6.4-inch HD+ Super AMOLED Infinity display which houses an on-screen fingerprint sensor. All of these smartphones are discounted significantly at Edgars this Black Friday. Click here to buy a Samsung Galaxy A-series smartphone from Edgars. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-451238" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/640x430_A30S.jpg" alt="640x430_A30S" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/640x430_A30S.jpg 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/640x430_A30S-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> This article wa